name: Austin Surfboards Gift Certificate
description: Consider yourself gifted!  With an Austin Surfboards gift certificate, you'll feel truly gifted.  Use it for surfboards, accessories, t-shirts or anything else in the shop!  Free shipping to any address in the contiguous United States!  Please put the To and From information in a message in paypal.

name: Austin Surfboards Coffin Logo Longsleeve T-shirt
description: Our coffin logo is our standard logo on all of the custom surfboards that we build.  A great classic and clean look.  This longsleeve t-shirt is printed in 100% cotton and pre-shrunk.  Available in white, black, and blue.

name: Austin Surfboards Cafe Racer or Bobber Zip Up Hoodie
description: This hoodie was designed and hand illustrated for our love of surfing and the open road on two wheels.  It is a very comfortable vintage style hoodie.  The only logo is the motorcycle on the back.  Available in green and gray.

name: Austin Surfboards Coffin Logo Camo T-shirt
description: A twist on our standard coffin logo T-shirt.  Blend in at your favorite hunting spot or just look awesome walking around town.  This is printed with blaze orange on a Real Tree APG 100% cotton, pre-shrunk t-shirt.

name: Austin Surfboards Beanie
description: Keep warm with an Austin Surfboards beanie.  These beanies come in a variety of colors, all with an embroidered Austin logo.  One size fits all.

name: Austin Surfboards Coffin Logo Pullover Hoodie
description: Our coffin logo is our standard logo on all of the custom surfboards that we build.  A great classic and clean look.  This is a heavyweight hoodie with hand warmer pocket on the front.  This is the Gildan Dryblend, 50% cotton and 50% polyester.  Available in black.

name: Austin Surfboards Camo Flex Fit
description: This is our Mossy Oak camo flex fit cap.  We have replaced the red in our coffin logo with blaze orange to match the style of the hat.  These are only available in the L-XL flex fit size.

name: Austin Surfboards Cafe Racer or Bobber T Shirt
description: This t-shirt was designed and hand illustrated for our love of surfing and the open road on two wheels. The back logo is the motorcycle and the front left chest logo is the skull helmet.  This is printed on a Gildan Softstyle 65% polyester and 33% cotton.  This style of t-shirt tends to run one size small.  Available in military green, red, black, blue, and gray.

name: Austin Surfboards Coffin Logo Trucker Flex Fit
description: This is our most comfortable hat.  The mesh back keeps you cool during summer months.  This hat is one size fits all.

name: Austin Surfboards Coffin Logo Sticker
description: Our standard surfboard logo on a peel-back sticker.

name: Austin Paipo Standard Size Green
description: The Paipo is our version of a foam and fiberglass bodyboard.  The advantage over the bodyboard is in the lack of flex, which gives you pure speed down the face of a wave.  Another advancement is the fins.  It comes with a  2+1 setup for maximum versatility.  The fins allow tighter arcs and drive out of the turns.  If you like to sponge, you will LOVE the paipo.

description:
The Soul Glide is a classic shaped nose rider.  This longboard has wide hips and a 19 inch nose for stability on the wave.  The Soul Glide has 50/50 rails with a belly bottom and a slightly rolled deck with a square tail.  Nose concave is standard and it has a slight tail kick.  This is the best all around nose rider of our longboard shapes.

name: Austin Fun Gun 13145 7'10
description:
The Fun Gun is our bigger wave step up board.  It is ideal for someone coming down from a longboard to ride something shorter.  Extremely fast and loose but maintains stability in larger surf.  It carries volume all the way through the board but most of it under the torso for ultimate wave catching ability.  It has an accentuated late nose rocker to help with steeper drops.  Comes standard with a tri fin setup.

Dimensions-  7'10x21.875x3
